Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.73,0:02:03.35,Voice Manabe,,0,0,0,,Chào.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.65,0:02:10.57,Voice Others,,0,0,0,,Là quán mì mới khai trương gần trạm điện đó.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.57,0:02:12.07,Voice Others,,0,0,0,,Muốn tới thử lắm...
